&lt;h2 id=&#34;conclusion&#34;&gt;Conclusion
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;In the last few days there has been an explosion of scripts and small apps which can provide a status line for Claude Code. I decided to give it a try and do my custom one. I hope it can be useful for other people too ğŸ˜‰&lt;/p&gt;
